<p><strong>Sustainability &amp; Scalability</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Adoption and Scalability (10 points):</strong> Evidence that the innovation would be widely adopted and/or purchased and has taken into consideration user behavior and context, and could be manufactured, and distributed at scale across a geographic region where ASGM occurs.</li>
  <li><strong>Business and Financially Sustainable (10 points):</strong> The applicant demonstrates an understanding of how they will finance their innovation over time, if and how it will generate revenue, and what risks need to be mitigated in order for it to be viable.</li>
</ul>

